  "description": "Listed Building Consent involving modifications (repair/replacement/demolition) to existing Grade II Listed Building comprising\r\nLower ground - minor excavation works (to increase floor to ceiling height) to internal layout of  basement kitchen/dining including extension forward with formation of store area and replacement of existing front door with timber sash window and rear windows with glazed panelling with double doors leading onto outdoor terrace. \r\nGround floor -  internal alterations reinstating decorative covings and plaster works/timber balustrade; removal of existing partitions; lowering of rear roof and rear wall recessed; repair of metal grille and paving to the front of the building and replacement of front boundary railing with traditional style. Demolition of single storey rear store attached to main rear wall and outbuilding within rear garden \r\nFirst floor - internal alterations to bathroom and infill of existing doors; partial demolition and rebuild of first floor side element with matching brickwork and timber sliding sash windows front and rear; Second floor integral alterations to the stairs and infilling of existing door to form new bedroom.  Full planning application also submitted reference P2015/5313.",
